# AirFrasher
Project created during Cisco Live Milan Hackathon (3rd place winnder + Entreprise IoT winner)

AirFr√§sher is a smart control unit build up on the latest IoT-Technology. It determines the optimal composition of temperature, humidity and air quality and provides independent regulation without any intervention required by the user thanks to a 2D and 3D sensor network.

